race.description: Ladbrokes Spring Hosted Pots Mdn Plate
race.comment: FALSTAFFIAN (3) debuted in a strong race at Sandown Hillside and acquitted himself well, sticking on nicely for fifth behind Obucci and Miss Revealing. There's been winning form out of that race and with natural improvement into an easier maiden, he should go close. CAELIUS (1) resumes. He showed ability in his maiden preparation, starting odds-on before a spell at Pakenham having posted a good figure at his second start. He can improve this time around. WYANDRA (10) has just found one better in both runs to date, in the market both times. He can land in a good spot and prove hard to hold out. TEXTURE (8) wasn't far away on debut in a bunched finish and can be improved.
